    %span.emoji.mr-6 ðŸ“†
    Week #{week} of #48in24
  %h2.text-h3 We're featuring #{featured_exercise[:title]}
  %p.text-p-base.mb-6
    = featured_exercise[:learning_opportunity]

  - if generic_exercise.deep_dive_youtube_id
    .text-p-base.mb-8.font-medium.text-textColor2 ðŸ‘‡ Watch our Deep Dive with Erik &amp; Jeremy!
